name: Polyethylene Sheeting
short_description:
Clear Polyethylene Sheeting

Clear polyethylene sheeting comes on rolls up to 200 ft. in length. This plastic sheeting is commonly used as a vapor barrier, a drop cloth, or to cover and protect a variety of items.
summary:
Description

All rolls come on a 3” core, and up to a 6 mil thickness. Our clear sheeting comes with a milky transparency that is easy to see through. All sheeting comes folded in half on the roll.
All orders over 5 rolls come with quantity based pricing that offers great discounts from website prices. We can have custom sizes made with a minimum order required. Call our sales department to inquire about this product or any other packaging products we offer.

name: Orange Guard - 10M
short_description:
Husky Orange Guard

Husky Orange Guard Concrete Vapor Barrier
summary:
Product Overview

The 20 ft. x 100 ft. Orange Guard Concrete Vapor Barrier is known for its ability to withstand jobsite conditions and construction foot traffic. This vapor barrier is designed for projects that involve slabs on-grade that require the mitigation of moisture vapor through the slab. This vapor barrier can cover up to 2,000 sq. ft.

  • Premium vapor barrier
  • 10 mil thick
  • Yellow-color
  • Ideal for projects that involve slabs on-grade that require the mitigation of moisture vapor through the slab
  • Known for its ability to withstand typical jobsite conditions and construction foot traffic
  • Super low water vapor transmission rate
  • Covers up to 2,000 sq. ft.
  • Get the right coverage - click here for Home Depot's buying guide
  • Note: Product Packaging may Vary

name: Poly AM Tape
short_description:
Poly AM Tape

  • Floor-safety marking tape is made of heavy-duty poly vinyl with rubber adhesive that sticks tight and removes cleanly.
  • Tape resists abrasion, moisture, common solvents and weather.
  • Ideal for indoor or outdoor marking of traffic areas, physical hazards, emergency zones and work sites.
summary:
Description

Bright yellow color with thick, black diagonal stripes makes it perfect for color-coding (black/yellow for physical hazards). Flexible backing allows application to curved walls, ducts, low-hanging objects as well as floors. 3" core is made of 100 percent post-consumer recycled content and is biodegradable.

Product Information

  • Roll Size: 2" x 108" (36 yd/roll)
